        "purpose": "modern_jp_reading",
        "value": "但し此の銀米は、漂民迎送の入目、朝鮮関所に召し仕え候役々宛行の船貫銀、水夫飯米貫銀、その外公貿易に付き一体に諸入目かくのごとし／ただしこのぎんまいは…"
      },
      {
        "purpose": "english_translation",
        "value": "Note: this silver and rice cover the costs of escorting shipwrecked drifters, ship-silver allotted to the officials serving at the Korean checkpoint, sailors' provision-rice silver, and other public-trade sundry expenses combined, as above."
